in spite of their flaws.

1296
01:17:18,758 --> 01:17:21,228
It's kind of what they do with
us, when you think about it.

1297
01:17:22,961 --> 01:17:26,700
Coming from the guy
whose dad wasn't sort of racist.

1298
01:17:27,299 --> 01:17:28,735
That's true.

1299
