We're still technically married.

1310
01:18:54,420 --> 01:18:55,922
Right. [CHUCKLES]

1311
01:18:56,388 --> 01:18:58,223
I just...

1312
01:18:58,256 --> 01:19:01,294
[SIGHS] I don't want
to complicate things.

1313
01:19:01,326 --> 01:19:02,594
You and... You and I,

1314
01:19:02,629 --> 01:19:05,098
