1328
01:19:42,934 --> 01:19:44,804
Forget all that stuff.

1329
01:19:47,973 --> 01:19:49,008
Are you sure?

1330
01:19:51,911 --> 01:19:54,080
Stop being so whiny.

1331
01:19:55,147 --> 01:19:56,850
