1382
01:24:26,384 --> 01:24:28,353
Honestly, I just...

1383
01:24:28,387 --> 01:24:30,523
I just wanted to meet here
because it reminds me of

1384
01:24:31,756 --> 01:24:33,093
how we felt

1385
01:24:35,193 --> 01:24:36,463
