1400
01:25:59,844 --> 01:26:02,615
Who carries pens anymore?
Everything's electronic.

1401
01:26:03,482 --> 01:26:04,551
[MADISON] Not this.

1402
01:26:06,018 --> 01:26:07,487
No, not this.

1403
01:26:12,957 --> 01:26:14,559
