I don't want to be here either.

1424
01:28:24,455 --> 01:28:25,523
But this isn't all my fault.

1425
01:28:25,557 --> 01:28:26,791
I never said it was
all your fault.

1426
01:28:26,825 --> 01:28:28,027
Why couldn't you put me first?

1427
01:28:28,994 --> 01:28:31,863
