1474
01:32:01,607 --> 01:32:02,808
[SIGHS]

1475
01:32:02,840 --> 01:32:03,875
Um...

1476
01:32:08,813 --> 01:32:09,848
Thank you.

1477
01:32:12,317 --> 01:32:14,820
